The invention discloses a bedstead structure of an overturning bed cabinet, which comprises a frame, legs, leg joint shafts, a bedstead overturning device, a leg joint shaft fixing plate and an overturning device fixing plate. The frame comprises longitudinal beams, end horizontal beams and bed corner bends. The longitudinal beams and end horizontal beams are connected via the bed corner bends and made of bedstead frame section bars. The inner side plate of the bedstead frame section bars comprises an indent T-shaped groove distributed axially along the section bar. The fixing plate is inserted into the T-shaped groove. Each fixing plate comprises at least two fixing screwed holes distributed along the length direction of the fixing plate and the fixing screw of the leg joint shaft penetrates through the screwed hole of the leg joint shaft and is connected with the fixing screwed hole on the leg joint shaft fixing plate. The overturning device fixing screw penetrates through the screwed hole of the bedstead overturning device and is connected with the fixing screwed hole on the overturning device fixing plate. The legs and the bedstead overturning device are installed inside the longitudinal beams and parts and fixing screws are not exposed outside the longitudinal beams, thereby the bedstead structure has a concise shape and an elegant appearance.
